My theory on the inhuman appearanced servants is they are made exactly for whatever purpose they have. For example a floor cleaner might be sort of like a giant slug scraping up stuff on the floor of the castle and leaving a trail of nice-smelling slime behind whereas a fighter would look sort of like a suit of medieval armor as made by H. R. Giger and a butler would be sort of a skinny skeletal humanoid shape with far to many arms. The only things they would have in common would be lacking any reproductive system, rather they just grow out of the castle floor and utter obsessive loyalty to the castle owner in a weird stalkerish way.

All in all I really like this idea.







